snippet.title: Farm Together Release Trailer
snippet.description:
From the creators of Avatar Farm comes Farm Together, the ultimate farming experience!

Manage your farm all by yourself or open it to the public and start cultivating together!

Steam Store: http://store.steampowered.com/app/673950/Farm_Together/
Xbox One Store: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/farm-together/9mxsdjxfzq25

Music - "Golden Sunrise" by Josh Woodward. Free download: http://joshwoodward.com/
